723153f-a.text:
(1)
St. Nicholas Ave., east side, (right), south from West 167th to West 166th Streets. Also shown (left) is West 167th Street, south side, east from St. Nicholas, to and including Audubon Aves. The two 5-story houses appearing at the left are facing on the east side of Audubon Ave. bearing Nos. 29 and 27. This area is also known as Mitchell Square.
June 15, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
